40|$|The {{subject of}} this thesis is the {{analysis}} of <b>legal</b> <b>expenses</b> insurance in {{the conditions of the}} insurance market in Czech Republic. <b>Legal</b> <b>expense</b> insurance is consisted of legal and financial protection in case of legal dispute or client's defending claims. <b>Legal</b> <b>expense</b> contains also providing consultancy and legal aid by skilled lawyer. Thanks to <b>legal</b> <b>expenses</b> insurance costs resulting from legal dispute are covered. The thesis is divided into two chapters. The first chapter is focused on basic characteristic, determination of the koncept, historical development and also legal expense' s exception. In the second chapter I describe the situation of the <b>legal</b> <b>expense</b> insurance in the insurance market in Czech Republic. There is located description of the specific products and comparison of the offer of particular insurance companies...|$|R
