40|$|The <b>legal</b> <b>expenses</b> {{insurance}} {{represents a}} means of financial elimination of fortuity's negative effects. These effects are joined to law-suits and legal acts. The insurance serves for enforcement of law and client's rightful claim in a trial or in an out-of-court process and its insurance protection includes settlement of court costs, court fees, lawyers' and authorized experts' costs, etc. The {{first part of the}} thesis is dedicated to a general form of the <b>legal</b> <b>expenses</b> insurance and to a basic characterization of insurance products. The second part is focused on a premium written. This part includes an analysis, which describes a development and a meaning of the <b>legal</b> <b>expenses</b> insurance in the Czech insurance market. The last part of the thesis deals with insurance products of the <b>legal</b> <b>expenses</b> insurance and also with an analysis of products' offer in the insurance market in the Czech Republic...|$|R
